<Weakness xmlns="http://cwe.mitre.org/cwe-7" xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" ID="340" Name="Generation of Predictable Numbers or Identifiers" Abstraction="Class" Structure="Simple" Status="Incomplete">
         <Description>The product uses a scheme that generates numbers or identifiers that are more predictable than required.</Description>
